           <p>Kristi Meyers is a science nerd and student-professed tree hugger. 14 years of combined public and private school teaching experience. BS in Elementary education and MS in curriculum instruction and design. Always looking to integrate technology into the classroom to meet student individual needs and reaching students using 21st century communication skills.</p>
